# | GPLv3-covered+} program [-in order-] to [-release it under-] {+a coworker
# | at my company, have I &ldquo;conveyed&rdquo;+} the [-GPL?-] {+copy to that
# | coworker?+} <span class=\"anchor-reference-id\">(<a
